        {
            "html": "<strong>2. Step 2: Rosemary - Lemon Zest</strong><div class='step-images count-6'><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FZ2/7ZUA/KX4OUQ7X/FZ27ZUAKX4OUQ7X.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Rosemary - Lemon Zest' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FHN/SRBY/KX4OUQ80/FHNSRBYKX4OUQ80.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Rosemary - Lemon Zest' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FO1/CTC5/KX4OUQ81/FO1CTC5KX4OUQ81.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Rosemary - Lemon Zest' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FG0/WTOF/KX4OUQ82/FG0WTOFKX4OUQ82.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Rosemary - Lemon Zest' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FVM/MVBZ/KX4OUQ83/FVMMVBZKX4OUQ83.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Rosemary - Lemon Zest' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/F5C/76PR/KX4OUQ84/F5C76PRKX4OUQ84.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Rosemary - Lemon Zest' loading='lazy'></figure></div><p><strong>Étapes :</strong></p><ol><li>Remove lemon peel (either with a special lemon peel remover, but grating is also fine), finely chop fresh rosemary leaves. Rub lemon peel with salt, mix in chopped rosemary. Spread on a piece of parchment until it dries completely, then fill into jars.</li></ol>",
