            "html": "<strong>5. Step 5: Sage - Orange Zest</strong><div class='step-images count-5'><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FH2/3E4M/KX4OURBP/FH23E4MKX4OURBP.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Sage - Orange Zest' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FH4/09U7/KX4OURBQ/FH409U7KX4OURBQ.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Sage - Orange Zest' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FFR/R899/KX4OURBR/FFRR899KX4OURBR.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Sage - Orange Zest' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/F9J/T721/KX4OURBS/F9JT721KX4OURBS.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Sage - Orange Zest' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/F5U/OW5J/KX4OURFY/F5UOW5JKX4OURFY.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Sage - Orange Zest' loading='lazy'></figure></div><p><strong>Étapes :</strong></p><ol><li>Chop sage leaves and place them in a mortar. Crush with salt. Remove orange peel and mix in. Spread on a piece of parchment until it dries completely, then fill in jars.</li></ol>",
