                    "lien": ""
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "html": "<strong>7. Step 7: Prepare Brine</strong><div class='step-images count-1'><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/F1I/9T45/KX4OUURI/F1I9T45KX4OUURI.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Prepare Brine' loading='lazy'></figure></div><p><strong>Étapes :</strong></p><ol><li>Prepare a 3% brine (for 1 liter of water add 30 g salt), bring it to boil and let it cool to room temperature.</li></ol>",
