            "html": "<strong>8. Step 8: Prepping Veggies</strong><div class='step-images count-5'><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/F3V/OPXL/KX4OUUYU/F3VOPXLKX4OUUYU.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Prepping Veggies' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FKF/L3GB/KX4OUUYV/FKFL3GBKX4OUUYV.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Prepping Veggies' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FS3/CKK6/KX4OUV9V/FS3CKK6KX4OUV9V.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Prepping Veggies' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FUS/VYUG/KX4OUV9W/FUSVYUGKX4OUV9W.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Prepping Veggies' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/F6Z/O7BM/KX4OUV9X/F6ZO7BMKX4OUV9X.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Prepping Veggies' loading='lazy'></figure></div><p><strong>Étapes :</strong></p><ol><li>Clean (peel and wash) and thinly slice veggies (or grate them as a matter of fact).</li></ol>",
