            "html": "<strong>9. Step 9: Filling the Jar</strong><div class='step-images count-5'><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FSL/IOFN/KX4OUVFP/FSLIOFNKX4OUVFP.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Filling the Jar' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FLJ/ZIX0/KX4OUVFQ/FLJZIX0KX4OUVFQ.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Filling the Jar' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FPR/XUKF/KX4OUVFR/FPRXUKFKX4OUVFR.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Filling the Jar' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/F6A/EYZT/KX4OUVFS/F6AEYZTKX4OUVFS.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Filling the Jar' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FSA/SO6C/KX4OUVFT/FSASO6CKX4OUVFT.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Filling the Jar' loading='lazy'></figure></div><p><strong>Étapes :</strong></p><ol><li>Dump spices into the bottom of the jar. Press vegetable slices tightly into the jar up to the neck of the jar.</li><li>Slice another carrot into 0,5 cm thick slices long enough to be tucked under the neck of the jar to keep pieces of veggies submerged.</li></ol>",
